data.description: Adorable 4 bedroom property in Rockwood with NEW ROOF is ready and waiting for you. With farmhouse style interior and gorgeous wood island andcounter tops in the kitchen, this property will provide space to spread out with a large fenced yard and he/shed and she/shed for all your hobbies. One shedis already equipped with wood burning stove. Back porch has been plumbed to be finished out as a main bedroom and bathroom on the main floor. Don'tmiss an opportunity to see this one!
